532,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddae59cd56a9b5c61d0aebad1d8ee94f1015ad7a","tid":1048532,"uid":195438,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-07T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">話Nokia係大陸機班人係咪傻閪到以為Nokia真係賣咗畀富士康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？人地仲好地地係芬蘭玩緊通訊設備，HMD都係芬蘭公司</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:05:00.000Z","msg":"兩樣嘢嚟，手機業務畀咗人做啦<br />\n<br />\n2016年5月18日，微軟確認以3.5億美元的交易價格將諾基亞功能機業務出售給富士康。<span style=\"color: red;\">富士康將接管擁有諾基亞功能機品牌授權</span>，包括諾基亞功能機軟體，相關客戶服務和供應鏈協議合約；諾基亞則宣布將向<span style=\"color: red;\">芬蘭公司HMD Global Oy授予全球獨家專利使用權，允許後者在10年內生產諾基亞品牌Android手機和平板電腦。</span>"},{"pid":"f76a67ca62c0dd399540ebb6c89f3b8e9cfed61c","tid":1048532,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3d47f425cdeec828b0a4ecf18a0e895aa0f106b","tid":1048532,"uid":220721,"like":1,"dislike":21,"score":-20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:12:00.000Z","msg":"外媒狠批亂關後台程式，Nokia 情況最嚴重，大陸機次之<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/985711/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/985711/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/18/080431_2567655b8ff9a3bfec5ae6ebc6ec077f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F18%2F080431_2567655b8ff9a3bfec5ae6ebc6ec077f.jpg&h=6ad8cc0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"018668a58442914f9b476ba33ef24e7b85bd1b19","tid":1048532,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:21:50.000Z","msg":"原文：<br />\n[url]http://<a href=\"http://blog.headuck.com/2019/01/23/致nokia手機用戶-請刪除「小鴨幹線」，用返「小熊來/[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.headuck.com%2F2019%2F01%2F23%2F%E8%87%B4nokia%E6%89%8B%E6%A9%9F%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6-%E8%AB%8B%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%8F%E9%B4%A8%E5%B9%B9%E7%B7%9A%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%94%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%8F%E7%86%8A%E4%BE%86%2F%5B%2Furl%5D&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=26b23670\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://blog.headuck.com/2019/01/23/致nokia手機用戶-請刪除「小鴨幹線」，用返「小熊來/[/url]</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://blog.headuck.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/hnd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.headuck.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fhnd.png&h=4b39b286&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">真的100%沒有加料 ?<br />\n少年你太年輕了。</span><br />\n<br />\n「小鴨幹線」於2018年11月尾升級至符合 Android 8 標準後，在「小鴨幹線」的 Google Play Console 突然湧現了大批不同型號 Nokia Android 9 手機，向 Google 的當機 （學名為ANR） 回報，指在啟動攔截服務時出了問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://blog.headuck.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/anr1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.headuck.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fanr1.png&h=5d5cd5f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Context.startForegroundService() did not then call Service.startForeground()&rdquo; 問題，冠絕小鴨App的所有ANR錯誤回報，一個月收到超過 800 次<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://blog.headuck.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/anr2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.headuck.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2Fanr2.png&h=d3d3d215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">一入去此問題的詳情，全數是 Android 9 的 Nokia 機款</span><br />\n<br />\n同是 Android 9 的其他牌子，包括同是 Android One 以至 Pixel 親生仔，以至華為小米這些問題常客，都沒有此項問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n綜合各種跡象，推測問題的原因，很可能是 Nokia 的 Android 9 手機，<span style=\"color: red;\">加入了原生 Android 所沒有，極為進取的殺 App（或凍結App）功能</span>，以致攔截服務剛啟動，未有時間按Android 8 標準完成顯示 Icon 的動作（其實只須以 microsecond 計的時間），使被 Nokia 的殺手殺掉（或凍結），來不及完成Android 8 顯示 Icon 的要求。系統發覺服務沒有遵守要求，便會發出此項錯誤。<br />\n<br />\nDon&rsquo;t kill my App<br />\n經網上搜查，果然有App （Sleep as Android） 的開發團隊，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">發現 Nokia 手機同樣問題，更找來實機驗証。據其研究所得，Nokia 手機，預載了一間支那 Evenwell 公司出品，名為 com.evenwell.powersaving.g3 的App，以前所未見的粗暴的方式殺 App。</span></span>套用該開發團隊（Urbandroid）的描述 :<br />\n<br />\nThe problem only occurs on Nokia devices with Android Pie. Nokia started to bundle a toxic app (package: com.evenwell.powersaving.g3, name: Battery protection) with their devices by some Asian company Evenwell. This app kills apps in the most brutal way we have seen so far among Android vendors.<br />\n<br />\n該團隊近日更綜合經驗，推出了 &ldquo;Don&rsquo;t kill my App&rdquo; 網站 （<a href=\"https://dontkillmyapp.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdontkillmyapp.com&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=63224bfa\" target=\"_blank\">https://dontkillmyapp.com</a>），列舉<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">最差的殺App手機，以接近原生Android為噱頭的 Nokia，名列榜首。（而同樣為Android One 的 OnePlus，緊隨其後），竟超越了「深度訂製」的華為、小米。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">啱啱瞓醒，唔知 &quot;fix&quot; 咗呢個問題未？？</span>"},{"pid":"c60dc9c5d4b76afd06043dd63b72668025708428","tid":1048532,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:29:46.000Z","msg":"芬蘭手機預載中國 kill app <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文：<br />\n<a href=\"http://blog.headuck.com/2019/01/23/nokia用戶請刪除「小鴨幹線」，用返「小熊來電」/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.headuck.com%2F2019%2F01%2F23%2Fnokia%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B6%E8%AB%8B%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%8F%E9%B4%A8%E5%B9%B9%E7%B7%9A%E3%80%8D%EF%BC%8C%E7%94%A8%E8%BF%94%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%8F%E7%86%8A%E4%BE%86%E9%9B%BB%E3%80%8D%2F&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=d3ed8e11\" target=\"_blank\">http://blog.headuck.com/2019/01/23/nokia用戶請刪除「小鴨幹線」，用返「小熊來電」/</a><br />\n<br />\n續上回，用 Nokia 品牌的 HMD Android 9 手機，預裝 (中國的) Evenwell 的殺 App 程式，粗略看過其源碼，發覺似乎無時無刻都在尋找殺戮對象，包括手機啟動，任何程序啟動，網絡環境變更等，都會檢查是否要大開殺戒。<br />\n<br />\n基本上，所有背景啟動，都會即時考慮是否要立即殺死(不是禁止啟動，而是出世後觸發該程式，檢查是後才殺死)， 但亦有不會殺死的種類或情況，包括 :<br />\n<br />\n最近曾開啟(在 Recent List 頭)的幾個 App<br />\n預設的 SMS App (但沒有 Dialer App)<br />\nNFC 服務觸發的 App<br />\n正在有來電響鈴時，不殺任何 App<br />\n取得audio focus (正播放音樂) 的App<br />\n正在用 network 的 App<br />\nLive wallpaper App<br />\n有顯示 widget 的 App<br />\n預設 launcher<br />\n預先指定的內置白名單App<br />\n進程(process)名稱包含冒號，即App的非主要進程"},{"pid":"26e73724d7f99b6c9874089b2138e435cac0c447","tid":1048532,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-10T07:37:39.000Z","msg":"追查一下內置白名單有什麼(國際版)，發覺有一系列的第三方 App<br />\n<br />\n來源：<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/urbandroid-team/dont-kill-my-app/blob/master/killers/nokia/com.evenwell.powersaving.g3/res/values/arrays.xml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Furbandroid-team%2Fdont-kill-my-app%2Fblob%2Fmaster%2Fkillers%2Fnokia%2Fcom.evenwell.powersaving.g3%2Fres%2Fvalues%2Farrays.xml&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=be4b95ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/urbandroid-team/dont-kill-my-app/blob/master/killers/nokia/com.evenwell.powersaving.g3/res/values/arrays.xml</a><br />\n<br />\n源碼已被2月7日的 2 個 commit 移除，不過若懂git的話&hellip; ：<br />\n<br />\nru.megafon.mlk<br />\nkz.beeline.odp<br />\nru.tele2.mytele2<br />\nnet.seddev.callerunknownlocation<br />\ncom.app5.rakem.wahmi<br />\ncom.KatlinDev.fblikes<br />\ncom.nttdocomo.android.remotelock<br />\njp.softbank.mb.tether<br />\ncom.nexon.nxplay<br />\ncom.opplysning180.no<br />\n<a href=\"http://no.intellicom.app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fno.intellicom.app&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXtg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=df8e5683\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">no.intellicom.app</a>1881<br />\ncom.ms1881<br />\ncom.hthk.ThreeShortCode<br />\nnl.addcomm.afvalwijzer<br />\nde.eplus.mappecc.client.android.alditalk<br />\nau.com.aldi.android<br />\ncom.g